OL,3,CStolen motorhome and tractor units
OL,4,Cfound in 'chop shop' raid
OL,6,FA motorhome and two HGV tractor units
OL,7,Fwere among five stolen vehicles found
OL,8,Fat a "chop shop" during a police raid.
OL,10,FOfficers from South Yorkshire Police
OL,11,Fexecuted a warrant at Kiveton Park
OL,12,FIndustrial Estate near Rotherham after
OL,13,Fevidence several units were being used
OL,14,Fto dismantle stolen vehicles in order
OL,15,Fto sell their parts.
OL,17,FThey found the five stolen vehicles, a
OL,18,Florry on cloned plates and several
OL,19,Fparts from other suspected stolen
OL,20,Fvehicles.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
