OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1773778273
OL,3,CStolen motorhome and tractor units
OL,4,Cfound in 'chop shop' raid
OL,6,FInsp Darren Birley, of the Rotherham
OL,7,FSouth Neighbourhood Policing Team,
OL,8,Fsaid the estate had been a "hotspot
OL,9,Ffor criminality".
OL,11,FHe added: "We have recovered stolen
OL,12,Fvehicle parts from all over the
OL,13,Fcountry hidden inside the units, as
OL,14,Fwell as pallets of suspected stolen
OL,15,Fstock from online retailers.
OL,17,F"We know the impact car theft can have
OL,18,Fon people which is why it is vital
OL,19,Fthat we work with other police forces
OL,20,Fto trace stolen vehicles and dismantle
OL,21,Fthese chop shops."
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@RO]
